#: front-page.php:33
msgid "Civic Engagement Tools"
msgstr "Mea Hana Kūkākūkā Kīwila"

#: front-page.php:33
msgid "for the People of Hawaii"
msgstr "no nā Kānaka o Hawaiʻi"

#: front-page.php:43
msgid "Government information shouldn't require a law degree to navigate. Civi.Me makes it simple to stay informed, show up, and have your voice heard — in plain language, for free."
msgstr "ʻAʻole pono ka ʻike aupuni i ka palapala kānāwai e hoʻomaopopo ai. Hoʻomaʻalahi ʻo Civi.Me i ka noho ʻike ʻana, ka hele ʻana, a me ka hoʻolohe ʻia ʻana o kou leo — ma ka ʻōlelo maʻalahi, manuahi."

#: front-page.php:53
msgid "What matters to you?"
msgstr "He aha ka mea nui iā ʻoe?"

#: front-page.php:56
msgid "Browse meetings"
msgstr "Nānā i nā hālāwai"

#: front-page.php:167
msgid "The challenge"
msgstr "Ka pilikia"

#: front-page.php:169
msgid "Civic participation should be accessible for all residents"
msgstr "Pono e hiki i nā kamaʻāina a pau ke komo i ka hana kīwila"

#: front-page.php:172
msgid "People want to be engaged, but the barriers make it feel impossible. We're removing them."
msgstr "Makemake nā kānaka e komo, akā he pilikia nā ʻālai. Ke wehe nei mākou iā lākou."

#: front-page.php:190
msgid "Buried information"
msgstr "ʻIke i hūnā ʻia"

#: front-page.php:191
msgid "Meeting agendas are buried in PDFs across dozens of county and state websites with no consistent format."
msgstr "Ua hūnā ʻia nā papa hana hālāwai i loko o nā PDF ma nā pūnaewele kalana a me ka mokuʻāina me ka ʻole o ke ʻano like."

#: front-page.php:203
msgid "No timely alerts"
msgstr "ʻAʻohe hoʻolaha kūpono"

#: front-page.php:204
msgid "Residents find out about decisions that affect their neighborhoods after the fact — if at all."
msgstr "ʻIke nā kamaʻāina i nā hoʻoholo e pili ana i ko lākou ʻāpana ma hope o ka hana ʻana — inā ʻike lākou."

#: front-page.php:219
msgid "Bureaucratic language"
msgstr "ʻŌlelo aupuni paʻakikī"

#: front-page.php:220
msgid "Government documents are written for lawyers, not residents. Plain-language summaries are rare."
msgstr "Ua kākau ʻia nā palapala aupuni no nā loio, ʻaʻole no nā kamaʻāina. He kakaikahi nā hōʻuluʻulu ʻōlelo maʻalahi."

#: front-page.php:234
msgid "Who are my representatives?"
msgstr "ʻO wai koʻu mau lunamakaʻāinana?"

#: front-page.php:235
msgid "Most residents can't name their city council member, let alone their neighborhood board chair."
msgstr "ʻAʻole hiki i ka hapanui o nā kamaʻāina ke hōʻike i ka inoa o ko lākou lālā kūlanakauhale, ʻoi aku ka lunahoomalu papa ʻāpana."

#: front-page.php:254
msgid "Start here"
msgstr "E hoʻomaka ma ʻaneʻi"

#: front-page.php:256
msgid "Tell us what matters to you"
msgstr "E haʻi mai he aha ka mea nui iā ʻoe"

#: front-page.php:259
msgid "Pick the topics you care about — environment, housing, education, health — and we'll show you the government meetings and councils that handle those issues."
msgstr "E koho i nā kumuhana āu e mālama ai — ke kaiapuni, ka hale noho, ka hoʻonaʻauao, ke olakino — a e hōʻike mākou iā ʻoe i nā hālāwai aupuni a me nā ʻaha e hoʻoponopono ana i ia mau pilikia."

