#: front-page.php:487
msgid "Live"
msgstr "Ola"

#: front-page.php:365
msgid "Browse Meetings"
msgstr "Nānā i nā Hālāwai"

#: front-page.php:368
msgid "All public meetings — boards, commissions, and councils — in one calendar. Filter by topic, council, or date. AI-generated summaries explain what's on the agenda."
msgstr "Nā hālāwai lehulehu a pau — nā papa, nā kōmikina, a me nā ʻaha — ma hoʻokahi ʻalemanika. Kālele ma ke kumuhana, ka ʻaha, a i ʻole ka lā. Hōʻike nā hōʻuluʻulu AI i ka mea ma ka papa hana."

#: front-page.php:405
msgid "Council Profiles"
msgstr "Mōʻaukala ʻAha"

#: front-page.php:408
msgid "Learn what each board and commission actually does — in plain language. See who sits on the board, upcoming meetings, open seats, and how to participate."
msgstr "E aʻo i ka hana maoli o kēlā me kēia papa a me kōmikina — ma ka ʻōlelo maʻalahi. E ʻike i nā lālā o ka papa, nā hālāwai e hiki mai ana, nā noho hāmama, a me ke ala e komo ai."

#: front-page.php:445
msgid "Get Alerts"
msgstr "Loaʻa nā Hoʻolaha"

#: front-page.php:448
msgid "Subscribe to topics or specific councils. Get email alerts when meetings are scheduled — before it's too late to participate."
msgstr "E kau inoa i nā kumuhana a i ʻole nā ʻaha kikoʻī. E loaʻa nā hoʻolaha leka uila ke hoʻonohonoho ʻia nā hālāwai — ma mua o ka pau ʻana o ka manawa e komo ai."

#: front-page.php:489
msgid "Guides & Compliance"
msgstr "Alakaʻi a me ke Kūlike"

#: front-page.php:492
msgid "Step-by-step civic action guides plus compliance tools for agencies — Sunshine Law, public records, accessibility, and public participation best practices."
msgstr "Nā alakaʻi hana kīwila kēlā me kēia hana a me nā mea hana kūlike no nā keʻena — ke Kānāwai Lā, nā moʻolelo lehulehu, ke komo ʻana, a me nā hana maikaʻi loa komo lehulehu."

#: front-page.php:511
msgid "What we believe"
msgstr "Ka mākou manaʻo"

#: front-page.php:513
msgid "Information access is a community right"
msgstr "He kuleana kaiāulu ke komo ʻana i ka ʻike"

#: front-page.php:516
msgid "Every resident deserves to know what decisions are being made that affect their community — in language they can understand, at a time when they can still participate."
msgstr "Pono kēlā me kēia kamaʻāina e ʻike i nā hoʻoholo e hana ʻia ana e pili ana i ko lākou kaiāulu — ma ka ʻōlelo e hoʻomaopopo ai, i ka manawa e hiki ai ke komo."

#: front-page.php:534
msgid "Strictly nonpartisan"
msgstr "ʻAoʻao ʻole loa"

#: front-page.php:535
msgid "Civi.Me does not endorse candidates, parties, or positions on any issue. We present facts: what a bill does, who submitted it, when the hearing is. We provide tools and templates — never talking points."
msgstr "ʻAʻole kākoʻo ʻo Civi.Me i nā moho, nā ʻaoʻao, a i ʻole nā kūlana ma kekahi pilikia. Hōʻike mākou i nā ʻoiaʻiʻo: ka hana o ka pila, ka mea nāna i waiho, ka manawa o ka hoʻolohe ʻana. Hāʻawi mākou i nā mea hana a me nā kūmole — ʻaʻole nā ʻōlelo kūkā."

#: front-page.php:549
msgid "Everyone is included — no exceptions"
msgstr "Komo nā mea a pau — ʻaʻohe kūʻē"

#: front-page.php:550
msgid "We use \"residents\" — not \"citizens.\" We support all 15 languages recognized by Hawaii's Office of Language Access. We build for mobile and include a phone line for people who don't have a smartphone at all."
msgstr "Hoʻohana mākou i \"kamaʻāina\" — ʻaʻole \"kīwila.\" Kākoʻo mākou i nā ʻōlelo 15 a pau i ʻike ʻia e ke Keʻena Komo ʻŌlelo o Hawaiʻi. Kūkulu mākou no ke kelepona a me ka laina kelepona no ka poʻe ʻaʻohe kelepona akamai."

#: front-page.php:561
msgid "Cultural respect is not optional"
msgstr "ʻAʻole koho ka hoʻohanohano moʻomeheu"

#: front-page.php:562
msgid "Native Hawaiian sovereignty is a living issue, not history. We frame civic participation as community engagement — not blind deference to government structures."
msgstr "He pilikia ola ka ea Kānaka Maoli, ʻaʻole moʻolelo. Hoʻonohonoho mākou i ka hana kīwila ma ke ʻano he kūkākūkā kaiāulu — ʻaʻole haʻahaʻa makaʻū i nā papa aupuni."

#: front-page.php:573
msgid "Open source and community-built"
msgstr "Kumu hāmama a kūkulu kaiāulu"

#: front-page.php:574
msgid "Civi.Me's code is public on GitHub from day one. Civic infrastructure should be open to inspection, contribution, and community ownership. If we ever make a decision you disagree with, you can see exactly why — and you can help us do better."
msgstr "Ua lehulehu ke code o Civi.Me ma GitHub mai ka lā mua. Pono ka papahana kīwila e wehe i ka nānā ʻana, ke kōkua ʻana, a me ka nohona kaiāulu. Inā hoʻoholo mākou i ka mea āu e kūʻē ai, hiki iā ʻoe ke ʻike no ke aha — a hiki iā ʻoe ke kōkua iā mākou e hana maikaʻi aʻe."

#: front-page.php:589
msgid "Join us"
msgstr "E hui mai"

#: front-page.php:591
msgid "Help build civic infrastructure for Hawaii"
msgstr "E kōkua e kūkulu i ka papahana kīwila no Hawaiʻi"

#: front-page.php:594
msgid "Civi.Me is open source and community-driven. Whether you're a developer, a civic advocate, or just someone who cares — there's a place for you."
msgstr "He kumu hāmama a alakaʻi kaiāulu ʻo Civi.Me. Inā he mea hoʻomohala ʻoe, he luna kīwila, a i ʻole he kanaka mālama — aia kahi nou."

